      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>This small pink crystal glows rhythmically, marking the seconds <span>as they pass. Once per day as a reaction, you can use a timeskip crystal to slow how you experience time relative to others. Once activated, the next action you take is reduced as follows: you can perform a full action by taking a standard action, perform a standard action by taking a move action, or perform a move action by taking a swift action.</span></p>\n<p>Once you benefit from a timeskip crystal you become immune to the effects of any timeskip crystal for 24 hours.</p>"
